# Breast Cancer AI Research Platform Architecture

## Enterprise & Research Grade Architecture (Optimized for RTX 3050 6GB Laptop)

### Vision
Develop a research-grade breast cancer detection platform supporting:
- Mammogram analysis
- Breast segmentation
- ROI extraction
- Tumor classification
- BI-RADS assessment
- Explainable AI
- Clinical report generation
- Experiment tracking
- Reproducible research

---

## High-Level Architecture

```text
Streamlit UI
    ↓
FastAPI Gateway
    ↓
Inference Orchestrator
    ↓
Service Layer
    ├── Image Validation
    ├── Preprocessing
    ├── Segmentation
    ├── ROI Extraction
    ├── Classification
    ├── BI-RADS Prediction
    ├── Explainability
    ├── Confidence Scoring
    └── Report Generation
    ↓
Model Layer
    ├── U-Net++
    ├── ConvNeXt-Tiny
    ├── EfficientNetV2-S
    └── GradCAM++
    ↓
Data Layer
    ├── PostgreSQL
    ├── MLflow
    └── File Storage
```

